* [[John Eatwell, Baron Eatwell|Eatwell]], John and Panico, C. (1987 [2008]). &quot;Sraffa, Piero&quot;, ''The New Palgrave: A Dictionary of Economics'', v. 3, pp.&amp;nbsp;445–452. 
