*[[Fernando Vianello|Vianello]], F. [1989], &quot;Effective Demand and the Rate of Profits: Some Thoughts on [[Karl Marx|Marx]], [[Michał Kalecki|Kalecki]] and Sraffa&quot;, in: Sebastiani, M. (ed.), ''Kalecki's Relevance Today'', London, Macmillan, {{ISBN|978-0-312-02411-6}}.
* Anderaos de Araujo Fabio., &quot;Sraffa and the Labour Theory of Value - a note&quot;, Brazilian Journal of Political Economy, Oct-Dec 2019, vol 39, p.&amp;nbsp;614-637.
*Santucci, A. A., 2010. ''Antonio Gramsci''. NYU Press. Chapter &quot;The Prison Notebooks&quot; (pp.&amp;nbsp;135–161) documents Sraffa's relationship with [[Antonio Gramsci]], while the latter was imprisoned under the Fascist Regime.

